name: INSERT_to_dataMachineTable
func:
msg.topic = "INSERT INTO dataMachine VALUES (" + msg.payload.machineID + ",'" + msg.payload.level.toUpperCase() + "','" + msg.payload.aisle.toUpperCase() + "'," + msg.payload.slot0 + "," + msg.payload.slot1 + "," + msg.payload.slot2 + ")"
return msg;

name: UPDATE_to_dataSensorTable
func:
msg.topic = "UPDATE dataSensor SET state0 = 0,state1 = 0,state2 = 0,timestamp = 0 WHERE machineID = " + msg.payload.machineID + "";
return msg;

name: UPDATE_to_dataMachineTable
func:
msg.topic = "UPDATE dataMachine SET level = '" + msg.payload.level.toUpperCase() + "',aisle = '" + msg.payload.aisle.toUpperCase() + "',slot0 = " + msg.payload.slot0 + ",slot1 = " + msg.payload.slot1 + ",slot2 = " + msg.payload.slot2 + " WHERE machineID = " + msg.payload.machineID + "" ;
return msg;
